[{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0038","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0038.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-53645","title":"Zimbra Collaboration Suite 管理控制台远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Zimbra Collaboration Suite (ZCS) 的管理控制台在处理包含大量逗号分隔路径段的 GET 请求时存在不当处理漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制请求，触发冗余处理并生成膨胀的响应，导致目标系统资源被过度消耗，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 ZCS 9.0.0 Patch 46 之前版本、10.0.15 之前版本及 10.1.9 之前版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2025-53645"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-07-09T17:15:31.297","updated":"2026-06-17T09:38:37.957","remediation":"升级 Zimbra Collaboration Suite 至 9.0.0 Patch 46、10.0.15 或 10.1.9 及以上版本。如无法立即升级，可在反向代理或 WAF 层面限制对 Admin Console 路径的 GET 请求长度，过滤包含过多逗号分隔路径段的请求以缓解资源消耗。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://wiki.zimbra.com/wiki/Security_Center","https://wiki.zimbra.com/wiki/Zimbra_Releases/10.0.15#Security_Fixes","https://wiki.zimbra.com/wiki/Zimbra_Releases/10.1.9#Security_Fixes","https://wiki.zimbra.com/wiki/Zimbra_Releases/9.0.0/P46#Security_Fixes","https://wiki.zimbra.com/wiki/Zimbra_Responsible_Disclosure_Policy","https://wiki.zimbra.com/wiki/Zimbra_Security_Advisories","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2025/53xxx/CVE-2025-53645.json","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/7614318c7ea4c24f707447d3fff16042945e6e08/2025/53xxx/CVE-2025-53645.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2025-53645.md","https://github.com/adysec/hwpoc/blob/7f9d328c5fbc6b96e5e86ea6c9dab85e4e384533/docs/2025/zimbra_zimbracollaboration-suite-%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-cve-2025-53645.toml","https://github.com/Hashmire/cpeApplicabilityGeneratorPages/blob/4588dccb1f913705444975eb2a5eb79962bf2513/generated_pages/CVE-2025-53645.html","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2025/07/GHSA-92rg-2wcj-32jv/GHSA-92rg-2wcj-32jv.json","