igation-script-heap-based-buffer-overflow-in-windows-spnego-extended-negotiation","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-47981.md","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/3f7b36031f03dbbe570abbcfed8c4b66874bb4dc/2025/CVE-2025-47981.json","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/a7fcebc1b9e9a88d443be844dae279be54e22ef4/data/2025/CVE-2025-47981-barbaraogmgf_CVE-2025-47981-POC.md","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/aaa966adf56b88bf2eba7f47ee24a777c6208719/2025/CVE-2025-47981/README.md","https://github.com/4ESTSEC/wxvl/blob/26b15b25c2543f872c330110db4ab2967c7c33e0/doc/2025-07/%E3%80%90%E9%A6%96%E5%8F%91%E5%A4%8D%E7%8E%B0%E3%80%91Windows%20NEGOEX%20%E8%A0%95%E8%99%AB%E7%BA%A7%E9%AB%98%E5%8D%B1%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-2025-47981).md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/2025/47xxx/CVE-2025-47981.json","https://github.com/TonneauBenjamin/ANSSI_Project/blob/f0e2d5e8be75f0351e759642d04d728399b4faa9/data/raw/first/CVE-2025-47981","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/8854c056beab250ba690e2bcc8887feb4c1f8139/2025/CVE-2025-47981/poc.py","https://github.com/DefectDojo/django-DefectDojo/blob/d9905eb7656178d3e59e0bf8f1d53a9ee9e50186/unittests/scans/openvas/report_detail_v2.csv","https://github.com/adysec/hwpoc/blob/333a12945888842887b9d7f35a124feef86df7c3/docs/2025/%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF_windows-%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-cve-2025-47981.toml","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-47981"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0027.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0017","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0017.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-32023","title":"Redis HyperLogLog 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Redis 开源内存数据库的 hyperloglog 操作中存在越界写入漏洞，经过身份认证的攻击者可向 Redis 服务发送特制的字符串触发堆栈越界写入，进而导致远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 Redis 2.8 至 8.0.3、7.4.5、7.2.10 及 6.2.19 之前的所有版本，CVSS 评分 7.0，危害等级高。建议升级至修复版本或通过 ACL 限制 hyperloglog 命令以缓解风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.0,"aliases":["CVE-2025-32023"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-07-07T16:15:22.830","updated":"2026-06-17T09:11:20.273","remediation":"立即升级 Redis 至 8.0.3 / 7.4.5 / 7.2.10 / 6.2.19 及以上版本。如无法升级，通过 ACL 规则禁用 hyperloglog 相关命令（PFADD、PFCOUNT、PFMERGE）作为临时缓解措施：在 redis.conf 中添加 `acl setuser default -@hyperloglog` 或 `rename-command PFADD \"\"`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/redis/redis/commit/50188747cbfe43528d2719399a2a3c9599169445","https://github.com/redis/redis/releases/tag/6.2.19","https://github.com/redis/redis/releases/tag/7.2.10","https://github.com/redis/redis/releases/tag/7.4.5","https://github.com/redis/redis/releases/tag/8.0.3","https://github.com/redis/redis/security/advisories/GHSA-rp2m-q4j6-gr43","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/52477","https://github.com/leesh3288/CVE-2025-32023","https://github.com/LordBheem/CVE-2025-32023","https://github.com/44528zja/Blackash-CVE-2025-32023","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-32023"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0017.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0047","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0047.toml","cve_id":"无","title":"若依 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"若依（RuoYi）后台管理框架的演示模块邮件接口存在任意文件读取漏洞。攻击者可通过 `/demo/mail/` 接口的 `filePath` 参数传入任意文件路径（如 `/etc/passwd`），由于服务端未对文件路径进行有效校验和权限控制，导致未授权用户可读取服务器上的敏感文件，造成信息泄露。该漏洞影响若依各版本，危害较高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["HWPOC-2025-00128a7f"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-07-03","updated":"2025-07-20","remediation":"建议升级若依至最新版本；在生产环境中禁用或移除演示模块（demo）；对 filePath 参数添加路径白名单校验，禁止包含 ../ 等目录遍历字符；对演示模块接口添加身份认证和权限控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/FeiNiao/ruoyi-management-system-has-arbitrary-file-reads"],"poc_urls":["https://github.com/FeiNiao/ruoyi-management-system-has-arbitrary-file-reads"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0047.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0036","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0036.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-53005","title":"DataEase PostgreSQL数据源JDBC连接参数远程代码执行漏洞","description":"DataEase 是一款开源商业智能与数据可视化工具，其 2.10.11 之前版本中存在 PostgreSQL 数据源 JDBC 连接参数绕过漏洞。虽然此前已对 socketFactory 和 socketFactoryArg 参数进行了检测过滤，但攻击者仍可利用 sslfactory 和 sslfactoryarg 参数绕过限制，通过构造恶意的 JDBC 连接字符串（如使用 FileSystemXmlApplicationContext 加载远程恶意 XML 配置文件），在未授权情况下触发远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 DataEase <= 2.10.10 所有版本，CVSS 评分 9.8，危害严重。官方已在 2.10.11 版本中修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.9,"aliases":["CVE-2025-53005"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-07-01T01:15:28.430","updated":"2026-06-17T09:37:27.673","remediation":"立即升级 DataEase 至 v2.10.11 及以上版本，该版本已修复 sslfactory 和 sslfactoryarg 参数的 JDBC 连接绕过漏洞。如无法立即升级，可在前端页面限制 PostgreSQL 数据源 JDBC 连接串输入长度，禁止包含 sslfactory、sslfactoryarg 等危险参数，并限制 DataEase 服务出站网络访问以防止恶意 payload 远程加载执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/dataease/dataease/security/advisories/GHSA-99c4-h4fq-r23v","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-53005.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2025/53xxx/CVE-2025-53005.json","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/87cc3b72f23339a3811f77c4104a170e7f34c37e/2025/53xxx/CVE-2025-53005.json","https://github.com/sec-dojo-com/cve-poc/blob/0d273a0b2821f58c8dfa9e9b4a2ad049f300e8ec/pocs/2025/CVE-2025-53005.md","https://github.com/adysec/hwpoc/blob/7f9d328c5fbc6b96e5e86ea6c9dab85e4e384533/docs/2025/dataease_dataease-%E5%90%8E%E5%8F%B0%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-cve-20