thub.io/blob/7583afdce3b666e3b7806f4edcd8058d5d07c2ea/archive/2025/2025-08-08.md","https://github.com/gelusus/wxvl/blob/0190a57b50c784bda47a3b9ac049eaf5bb577d6e/doc/2025-06/%E3%80%90%E5%B7%B2%E5%A4%8D%E7%8E%B0%E3%80%91DataEase%20%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E.md","https://github.com/anchore/nvd-data-overrides/blob/404b484bd5d19c483528cbf4559074858313076b/data/2025/CVE-2025-53004.json","https://github.com/kidrek/VigilIntel/blob/f9ffcf3da41d874caa7ad387f78fc1491e0799a2/2025/07/2025-07-02-report.md","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-53004"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2025/POC-AVE-2025-0035.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0035.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0066","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0066.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-32463","title":"Sudo chroot 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Sudo 1.9.17p1 之前版本存在安全配置缺陷，本地攻击者可通过 --chroot 选项结合用户控制的 /etc/nsswitch.conf 文件，在 chroot 环境中触发 NSS（名称服务切换）库机制加载恶意共享对象，从而获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Linux 系统上的 Sudo 程序，攻击者需具备本地用户权限即可利用，CVSS 评分 9.3，危害等级严重。Sudo 官方已在 1.9.17p1 版本中修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-2025-32463"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-06-30T21:15:30.257","updated":"2026-06-17T09:12:02.147","remediation":"升级 sudo 至 1.9.17p1 及以上版本。对于无法立即升级的系统，可限制用户使用 `sudo --chroot` 选项的权限，通过 `/etc/sudoers` 移除或注释掉不必要的 chroot 规则，或使用 `!chroot` 禁用该功能。如无需 chroot 功能，可卸载 sudo 并改用 doas 作为替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://access.redhat.com/security/cve/cve-2025-32463","https://bugs.gentoo.org/show_bug.cgi?id=CVE-2025-32463","https://explore.alas.aws.amazon.com/CVE-2025-32463.html","https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2025-32463","https://ubuntu.com/security/notices/USN-7604-1","https://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2025/06/30/3","https://www.secpod.com/blog/sudo-lpe-vulnerabilities-resolved-what-you-need-to-know-about-cve-2025-32462-and-cve-2025-32463/","https://www.stratascale.com/vulnerability-alert-CVE-2025-32463-sudo-chroot","https://www.sudo.ws/releases/changelog/","https://www.sudo.ws/security/advisories/","https://www.sudo.ws/security/advisories/chroot_bug/","https://www.suse.com/security/cve/CVE-2025-32463.html","https://www.suse.com/support/update/announcement/2025/suse-su-202502177-1/","https://www.vicarius.io/vsociety/posts/cve-2025-32463-detect-sudo-vulnerability","https://www.vicarius.io/vsociety/posts/cve-2025-32463-mitigate-sudo-vulnerability","https://iototsecnews.jp/2025/07/01/linux-sudo-chroot-vulnerability-enables-hackers-to-elevate-privileges-to-root/","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?field_cve=CVE-2025-32463","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/52352","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/code/cves/2025/CVE-2025-32463.yaml","https://github.com/D3ltaFormation/CVE-2025-32463-Sudo-Chroot-Escape","https://github.com/pr0v3rbs/CVE-2025-32463_chwoot","https://github.com/kh4sh3i/CVE-2025-32463","https://github.com/MohamedKarrab/CVE-2025-32463","https://github.com/K1tt3h/CVE-2025-32463-POC","https://github.com/Nowafen/CVE-2025-32463","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-32463"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0066.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0018","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0018.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-32462","title":"Sudo 1.9.17p1 之前版本 host 选项本地提权漏洞","description":"Sudo 1.9.17p1 之前版本存在授权机制缺陷，当 sudoers 配置文件中指定的主机既非当前主机也非 ALL 时，被授权的用户可在非预期主机上执行命令，导致越权访问。攻击者利用此漏洞可绕过主机级别的访问控制限制，在未授权的主机上以提权用户身份执行任意命令。该漏洞影响所有使用受影响版本 sudo 的 Linux/Unix 系统，CVSS 评分 2.8，危害等级低。建议升级至 sudo 1.9.17p1 或更高版本修复。","severity":"LOW","score":2.8,"aliases":["CVE-2025-32462"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-06-30T21:15:30.080","updated":"2026-07-14T13:17:33.347","remediation":"立即升级 sudo 至 1.9.17p1 或更高版本（各发行版已发布更新：Ubuntu USN-7604-1、Debian DSA、Gentoo）。同时检查 /etc/sudoers 及 /etc/sudoers.d/ 下所有规则，避免使用非当前主机且非 ALL 的 Host_List 条目，确保主机限制精确匹配。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://access.redhat.com/security/cve/cve-2025-32462","https://bugs.gentoo.org/show_bug.cgi?id=CVE-2025-32462","https://explore.alas.aws.amazon.com/CVE-2025-32462.html","https://lists.debian.org/debian-security-announce/2025/msg00118.html","https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2025-32462","https://ubuntu.com/security/notices/USN-7604-1","https://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2025/06/30/2","https://www.secpod.com/blog/sudo-lpe-vulnerabilities-resolved-what-you-need-to-know-about-cve-2025-32462-and-cve-2025-32463/","https://www.stratascale.com/vulnerability-alert-CVE-2025-32462-sudo-host","https://www.sudo.ws/releases/changelog/","https://www.sudo.ws/security/advisories/","https://www.sudo.ws/security/advisories/host_any/","https://www.suse.com/security/cve/CVE-2025-32462.html","https://lists.debian.org/debian-lts-announce/2025/06/msg00033.html","https://cert-portal.siemens.com/productcert/html/ssa-585531.html","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/52354","https://github.com/Hacksparo/CVE-2025-32462","https://github.com/CryingN/CVE-2025-32462","https://github.com/AdityaBhatt3010/Sudo-Privilege-Escalation-Linux-CVE-2025-32463-and-CVE-2025-32462","https://github.com/0p5cur/CVE-2025-32462-POC","https://github.com/MAAYTHM/CVE-2025-32462_32463-Lab","https://github.com/SpongeBob-369/cve-2025-32462","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-32462"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0018.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0031","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0031.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-49493","title":"Akamai CloudTest SOAP XXE注入漏洞","description":"Akamai CloudTest 60 2025.06.02 之前版本存在 XML 外部实体（XXE）注入漏洞，位于 /concerto/services/RepositoryService 的 SOAP 接口中。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向受影响版本发送特制的 XML 请求，利用 XXE 注入实现任意文件包含或服务器端请求伪造（SSRF），可能导致敏感信息泄露。CVSS 评分 5.8，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.8,"aliases":["CVE-2025-49493"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-06-30T20:15:25.060","updated":"2026-06-17T09:31:23.293","remediation":"升级 Akamai CloudTest 至 60 2025.06.02 (12988) 或更高版本，该版本已修复 XXE 注入漏洞。如无法立即升级，可在 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）层面添加规则，拦截 POST /concerto/services/RepositoryService 请求中 Content-Type 为 text/xml 且包含外部实体引用的恶意 XML 载荷，同时禁用后端 XML 解析器的外部实体解析功能（设置 DocumentBuilderFactory 的 setExpandEntityReferences(false) 和 setFeature(\"http://apache.org/xml/features/disallow-doctype-decl\", true)）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://techdocs.akamai.com/cloudtest/changelog/june-2-2025-enhancements-and-bug-fixes/","https://www.akamai.com/products/cloudtest","https://github.com/SystemVll/CVE-2025-49493","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-49493.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-49493.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/f8a21b0c30953d5926478bb080c200645e84a23a/2025/CVE-2025-49493.json","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/d09fb918849614ec417315b66ba20a16a39f16a4/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-49493.yaml","https://github.com/gobysec/GobyVuls/blob/a5de8e3be10d51a94e0977ecd8086c176251229f/Akamai%20CloudTest%20XML%20External%20Entity%20Injection%20Vulnerability%20(CVE-2025-49493).md","https://github.com/SourByte05/Vulnerability-Wiki-PoC/blob/e52a2c3eaf2fb0befc721cf0919d07ea435a23b4/2025/AkamaiCloudTestSOAP-CVE-2025-49493-XML%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5/AkamaiCloudTestSOAP-CVE-2025-49493-XML%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5.md","https://github.com/Threekiii/CVE/blob/b15267648d6c329465c8b4cfbeb7597850ead8c1/2025/2025.07/CVE-2025-49493%EF%BC%9AAkamai%20CloudTest%20soap%20XXE%20%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E.md","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/a7fcebc1b9e9a88d443be844dae279be54e22ef4/data/2025/CVE-2025-49493-B1ack4sh_Blackash-CVE-2025-49493.md","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2025/CVE-2025-49493.rules","https://github.com/cloudflare/cloudflare-docs/blob/368e16ffd3e2fe129ba5fa6b7b6c4ffb42daf854/src/content/changelog/waf/2025-07-21-waf-release.mdx","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2025/49xxx/CVE-2025-49493.json","https://github.com/sh4den/CVE-2025-49493","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-49493"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2025/POC-AVE-2025-0031.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2025/EXP-AVE-2025-0031.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0031.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0111","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0111.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-6543","title":"Citrix NetScaler ADC 和 NetScaler Gateway 内存溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Citrix NetScaler ADC 与 NetScaler Gateway 存在内存溢出漏洞（CWE-119），当设备被配置为网关（VPN 虚拟服务器、ICA 代理、CVPN、RDP 代理）或 AAA 虚拟服务器时，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过发送特制请求触发内存溢出，导致非预期控制流和拒绝服务，严重情况下可导致远程代码执行。CVSS 评分 9.2，危害等级严重，建议尽快安装官方安全更新。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.2,"aliases":["CVE-2025-6543"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-06-25T13:15:27.293","updated":"2026-06-17T10:02:07.007","remediation":"立即将 NetScaler ADC 和 NetScaler Gateway 升级至以下安全版本：14.1 升级到 14.1-47.46 及以上，13.1 升级到 13.1-59.19 及以上，13.1 FIPS/NDcPP 升级到 13.1-37.236 及以上。该漏洞已被 CISA 列入已知被利用漏洞目录（KEV），须在 2025 年 7 月 21 日前完成修复。如无法立即升级，可临时在防火墙上限制对 Gateway（VPN/ICA Proxy/CVPN/RDP Proxy）及 AAA 虚拟服务器的外部访问作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://support.citrix.com/support-home/kbsearch/article?articleNumber=CTX694788","https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabili