EDR OS命令注入漏洞","description":"深信服终端检测响应平台（EDR）管理后台存在OS命令注入漏洞（CWE-78）。攻击者无需认证即可向`/tool/log/c.php`接口发送特制HTTP请求，通过构造`strip_slashes`、`limit`、`host`、`path`、`row`等参数注入系统命令，导致远程代码执行。该漏洞影响深信服EDR 3.2.16、3.2.17、3.2.19中文版本，CVSS评分10.0，危害等级严重。Shadowserver Foundation已于2025年2月4日观测到在野利用，建议用户立即升级修复。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2025-34041"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-06-24T02:15:22.820","updated":"2026-06-17T09:13:21.777","remediation":"立即将深信服EDR管理平台升级至v3.2.21版本（2020年7月9日发布）。可通过管理平台在线升级功能自动安装修复包，或从深信服官方论坛下载升级安装包后在系统管理→升级管理→平台与终端升级界面手动导入。该版本已修复此RCE漏洞及已知其他问题。国际版v3.2.15EN和v3.2.22EN不受影响。如无法立即升级，可在边界防火墙上限制对EDR Manager接口（/tool/log/c.php）的访问，仅允许可信管理IP连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://vulncheck.com/advisories/sangfor-edr-command-injection","https://www.cnvd.org.cn/flaw/show/CNVD-2020-46552","https://www.sangfor.com/blog/cybersecurity/sangfor-endpoint-secure-remote-command-execution-vulnerability","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-34041.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/2025/34xxx/CVE-2025-34041.json","https://github.com/wooluo/nuclei-templates-2025hw/blob/37e9617426e2a696c8c338b15df99abd6294a4eb/cve-2025-34041.yaml","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2025/CVE-2025-34041.rules","https://github.com/onewinner/Lightx/blob/66baef13ea408675c6c144ae6e01b1df0a9278eb/config/pocs/CVE-2025-34041.yaml","https://github.com/zzzteph/low-hanging-vulns/blob/e01cbd1436b3805fae6aac0fdbaa88371dfa18db/nvd/2025/CRITICAL/CVE-2025-34041/README.md","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/d2626315618f92c3b6f631256244cb094cbffa68/2025/34xxx/CVE-2025-34041.json","https://github.com/tanjiti/sec_profile/blob/325d4883b5fe156c18fd47e477e38a13d3899546/README_202511.md","https://github.com/adysec/hwpoc/blob/e2c3d33b7e2870449a687c9b1cfa4c48990c946b/docs/2025/%E6%B7%B1%E4%BF%A1%E6%9C%8D_%E6%B7%B1%E4%BF%A1%E6%9C%8Dedr-rce-cve-2025-34041.toml","https://github.com/0xMarcio/cve/blob/55853b6e755a0ecd08195e09435b787f0cba6bbe/2025/CVE-2025-34041.md","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-34041"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0020.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0019","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0019.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-34040","title":"致远 OA 任意文件上传漏洞","description":"致远 OA（Seeyon）平台的 `wpsAssistServlet` 接口存在任意文件上传漏洞。攻击者可在无需认证的情况下，通过 multipart 上传请求中构造 `realFileType` 参数进行路径遍历（CWE-22），将恶意 JSP 文件写入 web 服务器可访问目录，从而直接访问该文件导致远程代码执行。Shadowserver 基金会已于 2025-02-01 观测到野外利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。建议立即升级至官方修复版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2025-34040"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-06-24T02:15:22.673","updated":"2026-06-17T09:13:21.587","remediation":"立即升级致远OA至官方发布的安全版本（≥V8.1SP2或联系厂商获取补丁）。如无法升级，在Nginx/反向代理层配置规则拦截路径包含`/seeyon/wpsAssistServlet`的请求，并限制上传目录不可执行脚本文件。同时部署WAF规则过滤`realFileType`参数中的`../`路径穿越字符。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://service.seeyon.com/patchtools/tp.html#/patchList?type=%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%A1%A5%E4%B8%81&id=1","https://vulncheck.com/advisories/zhiyuan-oa-system-path-traversal-file-upload","https://www.cnblogs.com/pursue-security/p/17677130.html","https://www.cnvd.org.cn/flaw/show/CNVD-2021-01627","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/52490","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-34040.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-34040.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/f8a21b0c30953d5926478bb080c200645e84a23a/2025/CVE-2025-34040.json","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/010b0aa4fab18a47a1dfa699acc027ecfea23b55/http/cves/2025/CVE-2025-34040.yaml","https://github.com/e