19:15:23.727","updated":"2026-06-17T09:30:49.357","remediation":"立即升级 Notepad++ 至 8.8.2 及以上版本，该版本已修复安装程序因不安全的可执行文件搜索路径导致的权限提升漏洞。临时缓解措施：将安装程序下载到除 Downloads 文件夹之外的其他目录（如桌面）后再运行，且确保下载目录中无恶意可执行文件；此外可通过组策略限制标准用户从 Downloads 目录执行安装程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/11yeUSWgqHvt4Bz5jO3ilRRfcpQZ6Gvpn","https://github.com/notepad-plus-plus/notepad-plus-plus/commit/f2346ea00d5b4d907ed39d8726b38d77c8198f30","https://github.com/notepad-plus-plus/notepad-plus-plus/security/advisories/GHSA-9vx8-v79m-6m24","https://www.vicarius.io/vsociety/posts/cve-2025-49144-detect-notepad-vulnerability","https://www.vicarius.io/vsociety/posts/cve-2025-49144-detect-notepad-vulnerability-1","https://www.vicarius.io/vsociety/posts/cve-2025-49144-mitigate-notepad-vulnerability","https://www.vicarius.io/vsociety/posts/cve-2025-49144-mitigate-notepad-vulnerability-1","https://github.com/assad12341/notepad-v8.8.1-LPE-CVE-","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2025/CVE-2025-49144.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/f8a21b0c30953d5926478bb080c200645e84a23a/2025/CVE-2025-49144.json","https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/bc433784ede7dbd633c8f5b318929cce6dea621a/rules-emerging-threats/2025/Exploits/CVE-2025-49144/proc_creation_win_exploit_cve_2025_49144.yml","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/a7fcebc1b9e9a88d443be844dae279be54e22ef4/data/2025/CVE-2025-49144-Vr00mm_CVE-2025-49144.md","https://github.com/gelusus/wxvl/blob/0190a57b50c784bda47a3b9ac049eaf5bb577d6e/doc/2025-06/%E3%80%90%E9%AB%98%E5%8D%B1%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E9%A2%84%E8%AD%A6%E3%80%91Notepad%2B%2B%E6%9D%83%E9%99%90%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-2025-49144).md","https://github.com/4ESTSEC/wxvl/blob/26b15b25c2543f872c330110db4ab2967c7c33e0/doc/2025-06/[CVE-2025-49144]%20%E8%B6%85%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E5%A4%8D%E7%8E%B0notepad%2B%2B%E6%8F%90%E6%9D%83%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/2025/49xxx/CVE-2025-49144.json","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/aaa966adf56b88bf2eba7f47ee24a777c6208719/2025/CVE-2025-49144/readme.md","https://github.com/adysec/hwpoc/blob/7f9d328c5fbc6b96e5e86ea6c9dab85e4e384533/docs/2025/%E5%BC%80%E6%BA%90_notepad-cve-2025-49144.toml","https://github.com/Hashmire/cpeApplicabilityGeneratorPages/blob/4588dccb1f913705444975eb2a5eb79962bf2513/generated_pages/CVE-2025-49144.html","https://github.com/TheTorjanCaptain/CVE-2025-49144_PoC","https://github.com/b0ySie7e/Notepad-8.8.1_CVE-2025-49144","https://github.com/Vr00mm/CVE-2025-49144","https://github.com/0xCZR1/cve-2025-49144","https://github.com/onniio/CVE-2025-49144","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-49144"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2025/AVE-2025-0030.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2025-0034","file_name":"2025/AVE-2025-0034.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2025-52923","title":"深信服 aTrust 权限提升漏洞","description":"深信服零信任访问控制系统 aTrust 至 2.4.10 版本存在权限分配不当漏洞（CWE-732），由于对 ExecStartPre 命令的权限控制不足，具有低权限的本地攻击者可修改该命令参数，在服务启动时以更高权限执行恶意代码，实现本地提权。该漏洞影响 Linux 版本部署环境，攻击者需先获得系统普通用户权限方可利用，CVSS 评分 4.3，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.3,"aliases":["CVE-2025-52923"],"sources":["hwpoc"],"published":"2025-06-22T01:15:24.097","updated":"2026-06-17T09:37:17.257","remediation":"立即将深信服零信任aTrust Linux服务端升级至最新版本（>V2.4.10），同时检查并修复 /etc/systemd/system/ 下 aTrust 相关服务单元文件的权限，确保属主为 root、权限为 644（-rw-r--r--），非 root 用户不可写入。作为临时缓解措施，可执行 `chmod 644 /etc/systemd/system/sangfor* /lib/systemd/system/sangfor*` 并执行 `systemctl daemon-reload` 重新加载配置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://community.sangfor.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&tid=10842","https://github.com/r00t7oo2jm/cVetest/blob/main/p0c.sh","https://github.com/r00t7oo2jm/cVetest/blob/main/sangf0r-poc.pdf","https://mark